15.content:
Konichiwa everyone, as of today you're about hear the story of a team of heroic crime fighting sumo wrestlers who also do Karaoke whenever there's no crimes happening in Sumo City.

As people want to know more about Sumo City and everything including our heroes themselves well then all shall be revealed as our story's about to unfold.

The place: Sumo City USA a district formerly known as Japan Town that's located in San Francisco California as the area consists of big fat sumo wrestlers, as the district's current permanent sumo stadium can be found here as it seats a few hundred thousand visitors as Sumo City USA is the center of the Sumo world as the district also has a Sumo Karaoke business that's open to everyone.

The Time: Present Day.

The Story: One day our heroes were at their Sumo stable as Raggs a blue furred anthropomorphic dog was having a hot bath, Pido a yellow furred anthropomorphic dog and laid back surfer dude was weightlifting, B.Max an orange furred anthropomorphic dog was meditating, Razzles a green furred female anthropomorphic dog was doing some research on the internet and Trilby a pink furred anthropomorphic dog happened to be having a hot bath as well as Dumpster the cat a Grey furred anthropomorphic cat walked into the Sumo stable as he had a few invitations with everyone's name on it.

"I found these invitations that arrived in our mailbox as we've been invited to represent team USA at the World Sumo Cup tournament." Dumpster said as he handed out each invitation to everyone.

"About this World Sumo Cup where's it going to be held Dumpster?" Raggs asked as he stood up and got out of the tub he was in as he dried himself off as Dumpster handed him his invitation.

"This year the World Sumo Cup tournament will be held right here in Sumo City." Dumpster replied.

"Dude we've been invited to represent team USA? Cool man!" Pido said as Dumpster handed him his invitation.

"After all our years of hard work dedication and perseverance paid off." B.Max said as his invitation was handed to him." B.Max said.

"I'm at a loss for words." Razzles said as her invitation was handed to her.

"Oh boy it looks like we're gonna be competing on the biggest stage of them all!" Trilby said.

"Alright everyone since we've been invited to represent team USA, we're gonna have to train like never before. Now that I'm ready to train like never before how about you guys are you all ready to train like never before?" Raggs proudly asked.

"Yeah!" His teammates proudly said in unison as they were ready to train like never before.
15.title: Sumo City All Stars.
